(27, 'CSS的border属性', 'cssborder', '', '<h2>浏览器支持</h2>\r\n<p>所有浏览器都支持 border-style 属性。</p>\r\n<p class="note"><span>注释：</span>任何的版本的 Internet Explorer （包括 IE8）都不支持属性值 "inherit"。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>可能的值</h2>\r\n<table class="tbl" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>值</th><th>描述</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>none</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 1px #666 none;">定义无边框。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>hidden</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 1px #666 hidden;">与 "none" 相同。不过应用于表时除外，对于表，hidden 用于解决边框冲突。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>dotted</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>定义点状边框。在大多数浏览器中呈现为实线。</p>\r\n<p style="border: 1px dotted #666;">Demo(1px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 2px dotted #666;">Demo(2px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 3px dotted #666;">Demo(3px)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>dashed</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>定义虚线。在大多数浏览器中呈现为实线。</p>\r\n<p style="border: 1px dashed #666;">Demo(1px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 2px dashed #666;">Demo(2px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 3px dashed #666;">Demo(3px)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>solid</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 1px #666 solid;">定义实线。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>double</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>定义双线。双线的宽度等于 border-width 的值。</p>\r\n<p style="border: 1px double #666;">Demo(1px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 2px double #666;">Demo(2px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 3px double #666;">Demo(3px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 4px double #666;">Demo(4px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 5px double #666;">Demo(5px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 6px double #666;">Demo(6px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 7px double #666;">Demo(7px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 8px double #666;">Demo(8px)</p>\r\n<p style="border: 9px double #666;">Demo(9px)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>groove</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 2px #666 groove;">定义 3D 凹槽边框。其效果取决于 border-color 的值。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>ridge</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 2px #666 ridge;">定义 3D 垄状边框。其效果取决于 border-color 的值。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>inset</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 2px #666 inset;">定义 3D inset 边框。其效果取决于 border-color 的值。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>outset</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 2px #666 outset;">定义 3D outset 边框。其效果取决于 border-color 的值。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>inherit</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="border: 1px #666 inherit;">规定应该从父元素继承边框样式。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>描述</h3>\r\n<p>最不可预测的边框样式是 double。它定义为两条线的宽度再加上这两条线之间的空间等于 border-width 值。不过，CSS 规范并没有说其中一条线是否比另一条粗或者两条线是否应该是一样的粗，也没有指出线之间的空间是否应当比线粗。所有这些都有用户代理决定，创作人员对这个决定没有任何影响。</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-04-09 02:31:59', 1, '', '2011-04-09 02:31:59', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-04-09 02:31:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 20, 'CSS的border属性', 'CSS的border属性', 0, 2700, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(28, 'Joomla! 移除 Mootools 的方法', 'joomla--mootools-', '', '<p>Joomla提速，移除MooTools是明显有效的，但是在Joomla 1.6中，移除MooTools后，前台编辑文章时会无法提交，若对前台编辑文章功能有依赖，1.6不宜去除。</p>\r\n<h3>从Joomla 1.5中移除MooTools</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">//remove mootools\r\n$headerData = $this-&gt;getHeadData();\r\n$headerData[''scripts''] = array();\r\n$this-&gt;setHeadData($headerData);\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>此方法经验证有效，但对1.5前台编辑文章功能有影响。</p>\r\n<p>不过，相对来说，1.5的MooTools不太大，去除它，倒不如换用<a href="http://code.google.com/intl/zh-CN/apis/libraries/devguide.html" target="_blank" title="Google Libraries API">Google Libraries API</a>，这样就已经有很好的提速效果了。</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>从Joomla 1.6中移除MooTools</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">//replacing mootools\r\n$headerstuff = $this-&gt;getHeadData();\r\n$headerstuff[''scripts''] = array(''/media/ai/js/jquery-151.js''=&gt;''text/javascript'');\r\n$this-&gt;setHeadData($headerstuff);\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>本方法有缺陷：<br /> 1.前台编辑文章功能无法使用；<br /> 2.修改后生成的html会变为</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">  &lt;script src="/media/ai/js/jquery-151.js" type="t" defer="defer" async="async"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;  </pre>\r\n<p>也就是说方法是有效的，但写法需完善。</p>\r\n<p>1.6移除MooTools会使前台产生错误，所以不建议直接完全移除。</p>\r\n<p>由于引入了的MooTools库超过300K，如果同时还要使用其他库（如jQuery）的话，这个影响还是很大的，所以有必要继续探索移除方法。</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 12, '2011-04-13 10:17:48', 1, '', '2011-04-13 10:17:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-04-13 10:17:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 10, '', '', 0, 647, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(29, 'W3C 的 HTML4 默认样式', 'w3c--html4-', '', '<p>作为css使用的重要实例之一，w3c的html4默认样式表具有重要的参考价值。</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">html, address,\r\nblockquote,\r\nbody, dd, div,\r\ndl, dt, fieldset, form,\r\nframe, frameset,\r\nh1, h2, h3, h4,\r\nh5, h6, noframes,\r\nol, p, ul, center,\r\ndir, hr, menu, pre   { display: block; unicode-bidi: embed }\r\nli              { display: list-item }\r\nhead            { display: none }\r\ntable           { display: table }\r\ntr              { display: table-row }\r\nthead           { display: table-header-group }\r\ntbody           { display: table-row-group }\r\ntfoot           { display: table-footer-group }\r\ncol             { display: table-column }\r\ncolgroup        { display: table-column-group }\r\ntd, th          { display: table-cell }\r\ncaption         { display: table-caption }\r\nth              { font-weight: bolder; text-align: center }\r\ncaption         { text-align: center }\r\nbody            { margin: 8px }\r\nh1              { font-size: 2em; margin: .67em 0 }\r\nh2              { font-size: 1.5em; margin: .75em 0 }\r\nh3              { font-size: 1.17em; margin: .83em 0 }\r\nh4, p,\r\nblockquote, ul,\r\nfieldset, form,\r\nol, dl, dir,\r\nmenu            { margin: 1.12em 0 }\r\nh5              { font-size: .83em; margin: 1.5em 0 }\r\nh6              { font-size: .75em; margin: 1.67em 0 }\r\nh1, h2, h3, h4,\r\nh5, h6, b,\r\nstrong          { font-weight: bolder }\r\nblockquote      { margin-left: 40px; margin-right: 40px }\r\ni, cite, em,\r\nvar, address    { font-style: italic }\r\npre, tt, code,\r\nkbd, samp       { font-family: monospace }\r\npre             { white-space: pre }\r\nbutton, textarea,\r\ninput, select   { display: inline-block }\r\nbig             { font-size: 1.17em }\r\nsmall, sub, sup { font-size: .83em }\r\nsub             { vertical-align: sub }\r\nsup             { vertical-align: super }\r\ntable           { border-spacing: 2px; }\r\nthead, tbody,\r\ntfoot           { vertical-align: middle }\r\ntd, th, tr      { vertical-align: inherit }\r\ns, strike, del  { text-decoration: line-through }\r\nhr              { border: 1px inset }\r\nol, ul, dir,\r\nmenu, dd        { margin-left: 40px }\r\nol              { list-style-type: decimal }\r\nol ul, ul ol,\r\nul ul, ol ol    { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0 }\r\nu, ins          { text-decoration: underline }\r\nbr:before       { content: "\\A"; white-space: pre-line }\r\ncenter          { text-align: center }\r\n:link, :visited { text-decoration: underline }\r\n:focus          { outline: thin dotted invert }\r\n\r\n/* Begin bidirectionality settings (do not change) */\r\nBDO[DIR="ltr"]  { direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: bidi-override }\r\nBDO[DIR="rtl"]  { direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: bidi-override }\r\n\r\n*[DIR="ltr"]    { direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed }\r\n*[DIR="rtl"]    { direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed }\r\n\r\n@media print {\r\n  h1            { page-break-before: always }\r\n  h1, h2, h3,\r\n  h4, h5, h6    { page-break-after: avoid }\r\n  ul, ol, dl    { page-break-before: avoid }\r\n}\r\n</pre>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-04-13 23:47:56', 1, '', '2011-04-13 23:47:56', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-04-13 23:47:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"http:\\/\\/www.w3.org\\/TR\\/CSS2\\/sample.html","urlatext":"http:\\/\\/www.w3.org\\/TR\\/CSS2\\/sample.html","targeta":"1","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 22, 'W3C, 标准, CSS, HTML4, 样式', 'W3C 的 HTML4 默认样式', 0, 2677, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(30, '同类型首选工具', '2013-01-16-08-31-45', '', '<h3>Consolas字体</h3>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?displaylang=en&amp;id=17879">http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?displaylang=en&amp;id=17879</a></p>\r\n<h3>PsPad+TopStyle lite 3.1+<a href="http://www.emeditor.com/pub/rand_ads38d3/emed6004efx.msi" target="_blank">EmEditor Free 6.00.4</a></h3>\r\n<p>前端助手</p>\r\n<h3>WinHTTrack</h3>\r\n<p>曾经用过同类的网文快捕，但实在比不上这个开源的干净利落</p>\r\n<h3>Launchy</h3>\r\n<p>为了提高切换效率，试过VAIO Gate、Fences等各种组织图标的工具，最后发现还是这个不用点击图标的工具最快捷。</p>\r\n<h3>TortoiseSVN</h3>\r\n<p>曾经寻找轻量级的RapidSVN替换它，后来发现，还是右键菜单的TortoiseSVN最高效。</p>\r\n<h3>Precision Helper</h3>\r\n<p>我所用过的最好的CHM文档制作工具。</p>\r\n<h3>CCLeaner</h3>\r\n<p>软件功能不错，也可以方便的导出设置，比较令人讨厌的是升级频率太高，不过同类软件基本都有这样惹人烦的举动,关闭更新即可。</p>\r\n<h3>FastStone Image Viewer</h3>\r\n<p>优秀的图片查看和批量调整工具。</p>\r\n<h3>FastStone Capture</h3>\r\n<p>本文涉及的唯一一个收费软件，用于屏幕截图、取色，功能贴心、界面简约、美观。</p>\r\n<h3>PDF-XChange PDF Viewer</h3>\r\n<p>PDF阅读器，小巧、界面美观。</p>\r\n<h3>MultipleIEs</h3>\r\n<p>用于网页IE6调试的绝佳工具。</p>\r\n<h3>IcoFX</h3>\r\n<p>ico图标创建工具，迷你开源，用于转换和设计。</p>\r\n<h3>EDraw Mind Map</h3>\r\n<p>免费的流程图制作软件。</p>\r\n<h3>xampp</h3>\r\n<p>方便开发的AMP(Apache、MySQL、PHP)环境。</p>\r\n<h3>M3家财通普及版</h3>\r\n<p>很适用的家庭理财软件，个人认为比财智理财软件要好用！</p>\r\n<h3>OpenOffice.Org 3.2 或 LibreOffice</h3>\r\n<p>开源免费的办公软件。</p>\r\n<p>前者OOo3.2是Sun被收购前最后一版，被收购后的3.3，仅改了Oracle的Logo和信息，然后又易主给了Apache基金会，不建议使用。</p>\r\n<p>后者是Sun被收购后，主要开源团队转而建立Document基金会，持续开发的版本。</p>\r\n<p>对于文档文件，建议存储为开源的.odt格式。这个通用格式，在其他软件，如Microsoft Office和WPS中也可正常使用。</p>\r\n<h3>差点忘了提7-zip</h3>\r\n<p>装完驱动紧接着需安装7-zip,如果有驱动是压缩的，安装7-zip还需提前。<br /> 建议各位Windows用户在压缩时首选.zip格式，以方便自己和他人解压。</p>\r\n<h3>最后必须提到一点，软件不一定最新版的最好。</h3>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-04-14 07:24:44', 1, '', '2011-04-14 07:24:44', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-04-14 07:24:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 21, '', '', 0, 712, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(31, 'initMoving 函数', 'initmoving-', '', '<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd"&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"&gt;\r\n&lt;title&gt;SmoothMovingLayer Demo&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;\r\n//&lt;![CDATA[\r\nfunction initMoving(target, position, topLimit, btmLimit) {\r\n  if (!target)\r\n    return false;\r\n\r\n  var obj = target;\r\n  obj.initTop = position;\r\n  obj.topLimit = topLimit;\r\n  obj.bottomLimit = Math.max(document.documentElement.scrollHeight, document.body.scrollHeight) - btmLimit - obj.offsetHeight;\r\n\r\n  obj.style.position = "absolute";\r\n  obj.top = obj.initTop;\r\n  obj.left = obj.initLeft;\r\n\r\n  if (typeof(window.pageYOffset) == "number") {  //WebKit\r\n    obj.getTop = function() {\r\n      return window.pageYOffset;\r\n    }\r\n  } else if (typeof(document.documentElement.scrollTop) == "number") {\r\n    obj.getTop = function() {\r\n      return Math.max(document.documentElement.scrollTop, document.body.scrollTop);\r\n    }\r\n  } else {\r\n    obj.getTop = function() {\r\n      return 0;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  if (self.innerHeight) {  //WebKit\r\n    obj.getHeight = function() {\r\n      return self.innerHeight;\r\n    }\r\n  } else if(document.documentElement.clientHeight) {\r\n    obj.getHeight = function() {\r\n      return document.documentElement.clientHeight;\r\n    }\r\n  } else {\r\n    obj.getHeight = function() {\r\n      return 500;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  obj.move = setInterval(function() {\r\n    if (obj.initTop &gt; 0) {\r\n      pos = obj.getTop() + obj.initTop;\r\n    } else {\r\n      pos = obj.getTop() + obj.getHeight() + obj.initTop;\r\n      //pos = obj.getTop() + obj.getHeight() / 2 - 15;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (pos &gt; obj.bottomLimit)\r\n      pos = obj.bottomLimit;\r\n    if (pos &lt; obj.topLimit)\r\n      pos = obj.topLimit;\r\n\r\n    interval = obj.top - pos;\r\n    obj.top = obj.top - interval / 3;\r\n    obj.style.top = obj.top + "px";\r\n  }, 30)\r\n}\r\n//]]&gt;\r\n&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;style type="text/css"&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n}\r\n#head {\r\n  width: 800px;\r\n  height: 3000px;\r\n  background: #eee;\r\n}\r\n#gotop {\r\n  position: absolute;\r\n  left: 810px;\r\n  top: 50px;\r\n  background: #ddd;\r\n  width: 100px;\r\n  height: 1000px;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n&lt;div id="head"&gt;\r\n  웹사이트 헤더\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id="gotop"&gt;\r\n  &lt;a href="#head" title="상단으로"&gt;위로&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;initMoving(document.getElementById("gotop"), 50, 50, 50);&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt; \r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 5, 0, 7, '2011-04-15 09:52:45', 1, '', '2011-04-15 09:52:45', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-04-15 09:52:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 1, 'initMoving 函数, JavaScript, Snippet', 'initMoving 函数', 0, 2753, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(32, 'Joomla! 基础 SEO', 'joomla--seo', '', '<p>Joomla是我最喜爱的CMS，但是Joomla的新站相对WordPress的搜索引擎收录要慢的多，很多人因为SEO的问题而放弃Joomla选择了WordPress。</p>\r\n<p>做好Joomla网站的SEO不是一件容易的事情，但最简单的方法便是向SEO更优秀的系统学习。</p>\r\n<p>简单做到以下几点，就会有很好的效果</p>\r\n<p>1.把www非www域名重定向到同一个位置，不要同时用不同的域名访问同一个页面</p>\r\n<p>将以下代码添加到Joomla的 .htaccess 文件，注意把 MyDomain.com 替换成你自己的域名。</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">  ## Can be commented out if causes errors.\r\n  Options FollowSymLinks\r\n  # mod_rewrite in use\r\n  RewriteEngine On\r\n  RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^MyDomain.com$ [NC]\r\n  RewriteRule ^(.*)$ http://www.MyDomain.com/$1 [R=301,L]\r\n  RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} !^.*MyDomain.com [NC]\r\n  RewriteRule (.*) http://www.MyDomain.com/$1 [R=301,L]\r\n</pre>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>2.友好的url</p>\r\n<p>3.在Joomla的“全局设置&gt;&gt; META标签数据设置”中填写 “网站Meta描述”和“ 网站Meta关键词 ” 。</p>\r\n<p>4.为每个分类填上完整的"Meta描述"和"Meta关键词"。</p>\r\n<p>5.坚持Joomla网站的内容更新。</p>\r\n<p>6.要有信心。不断完善网站的设置，并丰富网站内容。</p>\r\n<p>Joomla的SEO弱于WordPress，但是Joomla强大的可定制性使我们可以改进它的SEO，以达到和WordPress相同的效果。</p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 12, '2011-04-15 12:34:37', 1, '', '2011-04-15 12:34:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-04-15 12:34:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 12, '', '', 0, 502, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(33, 'PHP 的5种字段及作用域', 'php--5-', '', '<p>PHP支持5种字段作用域：public、protected、private、final和static。</p>\r\n<h3>public 公共的</h3>\r\n<p>[英] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈpʌblik</span>]  [美] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈpʌblɪk</span>]</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>protected 受保护的</h3>\r\n<p>[<span lang="EN-US">prə''tektid]</span></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>private 私有的</h3>\r\n<p>[英] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈpraivit</span>]  [美] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈpraɪvɪt</span>]</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>final 不可改变的</h3>\r\n<p>[英] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈfainəl，ˈfaɪnl</span>]  [美] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈfaɪnəl，''faɪnḷ</span>]</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>static 静止的</h3>\r\n<p>[英] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈstætik</span>]  [美] [<span lang="EN-US">ˈstætɪk</span>]</p>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-04-16 06:34:19', 1, '', '2011-04-16 06:34:19', 62, 1, '2013-01-20 03:19:31', '2011-04-16 06:34:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 15, '', '', 0, 652, 'robots=\nauthor=');
