(39, 'PHP Filter 函数', 'php-filter-', '', '<h1>PHP Filter 函数</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>PHP Filter 简介</h2>\r\n<p>PHP 过滤器用于对来自非安全来源的数据（比如用户输入）进行验证和过滤。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>安装</h2>\r\n<p>filter 函数是 PHP 核心的组成部分。无需安装即可使用这些函数。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>PHP Filter 函数</h2>\r\n<p class="note"><span>PHP：</span>指示支持该函数的最早的 PHP 版本。</p>\r\n<table class="tbl" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>函数</th><th>描述</th><th>PHP</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_has_var.asp" target="_blank">filter_has_var()</a></td>\r\n<td>检查是否存在指定输入类型的变量。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_id.asp" target="_blank">filter_id()</a></td>\r\n<td>返回指定过滤器的 ID 号。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_input.asp" target="_blank">filter_input()</a></td>\r\n<td>从脚本外部获取输入，并进行过滤。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_input_array.asp" target="_blank">filter_input_array()</a></td>\r\n<td>从脚本外部获取多项输入，并进行过滤。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_list.asp" target="_blank">filter_list()</a></td>\r\n<td>返回包含所有得到支持的过滤器的一个数组。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_var_array.asp" target="_blank">filter_var_array()</a></td>\r\n<td>获取多项变量，并进行过滤。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/func_filter_var.asp" target="_blank">filter_var()</a></td>\r\n<td>获取一个变量，并进行过滤。</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>PHP Filters</h2>\r\n<table class="tbl" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>ID 名称</th><th>描述</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_callback.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_CALLBACK</a></td>\r\n<td>调用用户自定义函数来过滤数据。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_string.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_STRING</a></td>\r\n<td>去除标签，去除或编码特殊字符。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_stripped.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_STRIPPED</a></td>\r\n<td>"string" 过滤器的别名。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_encoded.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_ENCODED</a></td>\r\n<td>URL-encode 字符串，去除或编码特殊字符。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_special_chars.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_SPECIAL_CHARS</a></td>\r\n<td>HTML 转义字符 ''"&lt;&gt;&amp; 以及 ASCII 值小于 32 的字符。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_email.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_EMAIL</a></td>\r\n<td>删除所有字符，除了字母、数字以及 !#$%&amp;''*+-/=?^_`{|}~@.[]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_url.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_URL</a></td>\r\n<td>删除所有字符，除了字母、数字以及 $-_.+!*''(),{}|\\\\^~[]`&lt;&gt;#%";/?:@&amp;=</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_number_int.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_NUMBER_INT</a></td>\r\n<td>删除所有字符，除了数字和 +-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_number_float.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_NUMBER_FLOAT</a></td>\r\n<td>删除所有字符，除了数字、+- 以及 .,eE。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_sanitize_magic_quotes.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_SANITIZE_MAGIC_QUOTES</a></td>\r\n<td>应用 addslashes()。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_unsafe_raw.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_UNSAFE_RAW</a></td>\r\n<td>不进行任何过滤，去除或编码特殊字符。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_int.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_INT</a></td>\r\n<td>在指定的范围以整数验证值。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_boolean.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_BOOLEAN</a></td>\r\n<td>如果是 "1", "true", "on" 以及 "yes"，则返回 true，如果是 "0", "false", "off", "no" 以及 ""，则返回 false。否则返回 NULL。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_float.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_FLOAT</a></td>\r\n<td>以浮点数验证值。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_regexp.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_REGEXP</a></td>\r\n<td>根据 regexp，兼容 Perl 的正则表达式来验证值。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_url.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_URL</a></td>\r\n<td>把值作为 URL 来验证。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_email.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_EMAIL</a></td>\r\n<td>把值作为 e-mail 来验证。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/php/filter_validate_ip.asp" target="_blank">FILTER_VALIDATE_IP</a></td>\r\n<td>把值作为 IP 地址来验证。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 2, 0, 10, '2011-07-28 08:49:51', 1, '', '2011-07-28 08:49:51', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-07-28 08:49:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 386, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(40, 'IE6的BUG汇总', 'ie6bug', '', '<h3>IE6的div最小高度的BUG</h3>\r\n<p>在网页布局时常会用到 DIV 来显示一些边角背景，需要设置较小的高度，默认情况下，IE6 中设置 DIV 较小高度会不起作用，在 IE7、FF 等浏览器不存在这个问题。</p>\r\n<p>IE6 下默认的字体尺寸大致在 12 - 14px 之间，当你试图定义一个高度小于这个默认值的 DIV 的时候， IE6 会固执的认为这个层的高度不应该小于字体的行高。所以即使你用 height:5px; 来定义了一个 DIV 的高度，实际在 IE6 下显示的仍然是一个 12px 左右高度的层。</p>\r\n<p>要解决这个问题，可以强制定义该 DIV 的字体尺寸，或者定义 overflow 属性来限制 DIV 高度的自动调整。比如:</p>\r\n<p>&lt;div style="height: 5px; font: 0px Arial; line-height:0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p><!--more-->或者</p>\r\n<p>&lt;div style="height: 5px; overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p>值得注意的是，设置 font-size:0 时这个容器的高度最小为 2px ，如果要设置 DIV 高度为 0 或 1px ，则需要使用 overflow:hidden; 来实现。</p>\r\n<hr title="png24格式图片的透明度解析" alt="png24" class="system-pagebreak" />\r\n<h3>png24格式图片的透明度解析</h3>\r\n<p>png24格式图片的透明度解析</p>\r\n<hr title="IE6 列表 背景 消失" alt="li-no-bg" class="system-pagebreak" />\r\n<h3>IE6列表背景消失</h3>\r\n<p>IE6中设定了position: relative; float: left的容器下，如果存在着多个带有背景的列表，那么这些列表中有一部分会显示不正常，具体的表现为背景消失。</p>\r\n<p><strong>解决的方法是给li也加上position: relative</strong>。</p>\r\n<p>这个BUG的具体描述，请参考：<a href="http://www.positioniseverything.net/explorer/ie-listbug.html" target="_blank">http://www.positioniseverything.net/explorer/ie-listbug.html</a></p>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-07-29 04:27:38', 1, '', '2011-07-29 04:27:38', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-07-29 04:27:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 16, 'IE6的BUG汇总, CSS, 前端开发, IE6, Bug', 'IE6的BUG汇总', 0, 2890, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(41, '建立重设CSS的一些依据', 'css', '', '<p>重设css的作用，在我理解不是删除全部样式，而是建立相对统一的基本样式，以便在没有排版的情况下，可以有基本的美观度，同时一些细致排版没有涉及到的内容，也可以被它照顾到。</p>\r\n<p>1、body的margin和padding都需去除，ie的默认margin为10px，ff的默认padding为8px，不统一，所以需要去除。</p>\r\n<p>2、w3c为每个元素都定义了默认显示样式，我们需要把默认为块状显示的元素的margin和padding统一去除，这一步操作清除掉了所有块元素的样式，所以我们需要为常用元素重新建立统一的样式。如h1，h2，h3，h4，h5，h6，p，ul，li，ol，dl，dt，dd，table，form，img。</p>\r\n<p>3、列表样式，ie与ff默认都为左缩进40px。ie通过ul、ol的margin属性设置；ff通过ul、ol的padding属性设置。</p>\r\n<p>dl、dt无缩进，dd缩进为40px。</p>\r\n<p>而我们已经删除了全部样式，重设为li、dd{padding-left:2em; margin-bottom:.2em; margin-top:.2em;}，这样做的好处是列表可以占满盒子的完整宽度，同时设置{list-style-image: url(''square.gif''); list-style-position:inside;}这样可以把列表符号放在li、dd盒子的内部。</p>\r\n<p>4、标题，h1、h2、h3、h4、h5、h6分别设置上下margin、字号，值h1的最大，h6最小。</p>\r\n<p>5、链接，a，去除下划线，只在鼠标移上时显示下划线。</p>\r\n<p>6、图片，去除边框。</p>\r\n<p>7、段落，p，段首有2字符缩进，段与段之间有空一行</p>\r\n<p>8、表格table，</p>\r\n<p>9、hr</p>\r\n<p>10、表单元素</p>\r\n<p>11、b和strong意味强调，应设置为粗体</p>\r\n<p>12、字体的fallback，在首个字体不存在时，会自动fallback到下一个；当前字体中缺少字符时，会fallback到系统字体</p>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-07-29 23:50:43', 1, '', '2011-07-29 23:50:43', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-07-29 23:50:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 14, '', '', 0, 2484, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(42, 'Joomla! 1.5 表单 XML 文件编写参考', 'joomla-1-5-xml-', '', '<div class="article_content">\r\n<p>有关Joomla!1.5表单XML的使用方法和功能描述，请参考这篇文章：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;name&gt;Showcase Form&lt;/name&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;params&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;param name="catid" type="list" size="20" default="0" label="Category ID" description="Category ID"&gt;\r\n\r\n   &lt;option value="0"&gt;Public&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n   &lt;option value="1"&gt;Registered&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n   &lt;option value="2"&gt;Special&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;/param&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;param name="title" type="text" size="20" default="" label="title" description="title" /&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;/params&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p><br /> 我们看到每个param item都包含以下几项：</p>\r\n<p>name - field 名称<br /> type - field类型, text, a list box, etc<br /> label - form中显示的标签<br /> description - tooltip 显示的文字<br /> default - 默认值</p>\r\n<p>在一个params section可以书写多个 param</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;params&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;param ... /&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;param ... /&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/params&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>你可以在params处指定addpath，这个目录下放置自定义的element文件。（关于element的自定义我们另外说明）</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;params addpath="/components/com_contact/elements"&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;param ... /&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Joomla! core中目前已经提供的element 类型包括以下几种：</p>\r\n<p>文章分类选择列表</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="catid" type="category" default="0" label="Category" description="An article category" /&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>添加一个section 属性，你也可以选择其他组件的分类数据，比如下面的代码选择 weblinks的分类。</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="catid" type="category" section="com_weblinks" default="0" label="Category" description="A weblinks category" /&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>可视化编辑器：选择一个可视化编辑器</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="editor" type="editors" default="" label="User Editor" description="WYSYWYG Editor for this User" /&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>文件列表：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="file_name" type="imagelist" directory="/images/stories" filter="" hide_default="1" default="" label="Menu Image" description="PARAMMENUIMAGE" /&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>各参数定义如下：</p>\r\n<p>directory - 文件列表的目录<br /> filter - 过滤器，这是一个正则表达式<br /> exclude - 排除文件，一个正则表达式<br /> stripext - set to 1 to strip the file extension in the list<br /> hide_none - set to 1 to hide the ‘Do not use’ list option<br /> hide_default - set to 1 to hide the ‘Use Default’ list option</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><br /> Helpsites</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="helpsite" type="helpsites" default="" label="Help Site" description="Help site for this User" /&gt; \r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Imagelist</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="menu_image" type="imagelist" directory="/images/stories" hide_default="1" default="" label="Menu Image" description="PARAMMENUIMAGE" /&gt; \r\n</pre>\r\n<p>hide_default - set to 1 to hide an automatic Use Default entry in the list</p>\r\n<p><br /> 语言选择</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="language" type="languages" client="site" default="" label="Front-end Language" description="paramLanguage" /&gt; \r\n</pre>\r\n<p>List</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="link_titles" type="list" default="" label="Linked Titles" description="Make the Item titles linkable"&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;option value=""&gt;Use Global&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;option value="0"&gt;No&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;option value="1"&gt;Yes&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/param&gt; \r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Menu<br /> Menu Item</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="menu_item" type="menuitem" label="Menu Item" /&gt;Radio\r\n\r\n&lt;param name="cache" type="radio" default="0" label="Enable Cache" description="PARAMENABLECACHE"&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;option value="0"&gt;No&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n &lt;option value="1"&gt;Yes&lt;/option&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/param&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Section</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="sectionid" type="section" default="0" label="Edit posts" description="Set the section to retrieve posts from" /&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Spacer</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="@spacer" type="spacer" default="" label="" description="" /&gt; \r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Text</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="moduleclass_sfx" type="text" default="" label="Module Class Suffix" description="PARAMMODULECLASSSUFFIX" /&gt; \r\n</pre>\r\n<p>Textarea</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;param name="description_text" type="textarea" default="" label="Description Text" rows="5" cols="30" description="PARAMDESCTEXT"/&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>rows - the number of rows for the <br /> cols - the number of columns for the textarea</p>\r\n<p>我们最常使用的是 Text，Textarea，List,radio,hidden等</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 4, 0, 13, '2011-09-07 09:07:16', 1, '', '2011-09-07 09:07:16', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-09-07 09:07:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 512, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(43, 'Joomla! 1.5 和 2.5 模板的区别', 'joomla-tpl-15-vs-25', '', '<h3>1.文件差异</h3>\r\n<table class="tbl" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope="col">Joomla!1.5</th><th scope="col"> </th><th scope="col">Joomla!2.5</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>&lt;——&gt;</td>\r\n<td>tpl/language</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>&lt;——&gt;</td>\r\n<td>tpl/error.php</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>tpl/params.ini</td>\r\n<td>&lt;——&gt;</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>&lt;——&gt;</td>\r\n<td>template_preview.png</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>2.模板信息.xml格式差异</h3>\r\n<h4>Joomla! 1.5</h4>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE install PUBLIC "-//Joomla! 1.5//DTD template 1.0//EN" "http://www.joomla.org/xml/dtd/1.5/template-install.dtd"&gt;\r\n&lt;install version="1.5" type="template"&gt;\r\n \r\n	&lt;params&gt;\r\n		&lt;param&gt;&lt;/param&gt;\r\n	&lt;/params&gt;\r\n&lt;/install&gt;</pre>\r\n<h4>Joomla! 2.5</h4>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE install PUBLIC "-//Joomla! 2.5//DTD template 1.0//EN" "http://www.joomla.org/xml/dtd/2.5/template-install.dtd"&gt;\r\n&lt;extension version="2.5" type="template" client="site"&gt;\r\n \r\n	&lt;config&gt;\r\n		&lt;fields name="params"&gt;\r\n			&lt;fieldset name="advanced"&gt;\r\n				&lt;field&gt;&lt;/field&gt;\r\n			&lt;/fieldset&gt;\r\n		&lt;/fields&gt;\r\n	&lt;/config&gt;\r\n&lt;/extension&gt;</pre>\r\n<h3>3.模板功能差异</h3>\r\n<p>由于Joomla!2.5的xml字段多了图片参数设定功能，同时也增加了多模板套用。Joomla!2.5模板可以多增设一些更人性化的功能，因此会使tpl/index.php产生更多差异。</p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 12, '2011-09-07 09:46:26', 1, '', '2011-09-07 09:46:26', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-09-07 09:46:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 859, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(44, 'Joomla! 视图文件批量提取工具', 'joomla-views-batch-copy', '', '<p>想要重写Joomla!视图文件时，按规定路径在templates/tpl_name/html文件夹下创建对应文件是第一步。但是Joomla视图文件较多，这个创建过程着实累人，因此，<a href="http://www.bubujie.net/">步步街</a>制作了以下.bat批处理文件以方便批量创建便于自定义的视图文件。</p>\r\n<h3>Joomla 模块提取</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">@echo off&amp;setlocal enabledelayedexpansion\r\n\r\ndir E:\\htdocs\\j15\\modules /b /s /O:N /A:D &gt; mod_list.txt\r\nfor /f "delims=" %%a in (''findstr ".*tmpl" mod_list.txt'') do (\r\n set "str=%%a"&amp;set "str=!str:\\j15\\=\\new15\\!"\r\n echo %%a\r\n echo !str:\\tmpl\\=\\!\r\n xcopy %%a !str:\\tmpl=\\! /E /I /EXCLUDE:joomla_uncopy.txt\r\n)\r\n\r\npause&gt;nul\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Joomla 组件和模块同时提取</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">@echo off&amp;setlocal enabledelayedexpansion\r\ndir E:\\htdocs\\j15\\components /b /s /O:N /A:D &gt; com_list.txt\r\nfor /f "delims=" %%a in (''findstr "views.*tmpl" com_list.txt'') do (\r\n set "str=%%a"&amp;set "str=!str:\\j15\\=\\new1523\\!"\r\n set "str=!str:\\views\\=\\!"\r\n echo %%a\r\n echo !str:\\tmpl\\=\\!\r\n xcopy %%a !str:\\tmpl=\\! /E /I /EXCLUDE:joomla_uncopy.txt\r\n)\r\n\r\ndir E:\\htdocs\\j15\\modules /b /s /O:N /A:D &gt; mod_list.txt\r\nfor /f "delims=" %%a in (''findstr ".*tmpl" mod_list.txt'') do (\r\n set "str=%%a"&amp;set "str=!str:\\j15\\=\\new15\\!"\r\n echo %%a\r\n echo !str:\\tmpl\\=\\!\r\n xcopy %%a !str:\\tmpl=\\! /E /I /EXCLUDE:joomla_uncopy.txt\r\n)\r\n\r\npause&gt;nul\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>告知禁止提取项</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">.xml\r\n.html\r\n</pre>', '', 1, 4, 0, 12, '2011-09-10 01:38:46', 1, '', '2011-09-10 01:38:46', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-09-10 01:38:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 9, '', '', 0, 384, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(45, '一些软件的使用技巧', '2013-01-16-08-34-33', '', '<hr title="Gtalk多开" alt="gtalk-multiple" class="system-pagebreak" />\r\n<p>1.创建一个Gtalk桌面快捷方式</p>\r\n<p>2.右击Gtalk桌面快捷方式图标“属性”，转移到“快捷方式”标签</p>\r\n<p>3.在“目标”栏中，原来的GTalk目标位置后面增加“/nomutex”命令即可，比如我的：<br /> "C:\\Program Files\\Google\\Google Talk\\googletalk.exe" /nomutex （exe"与/nomutex之间有空格）</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-09-10 01:38:46', 1, '', '2011-09-10 01:38:46', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-09-10 01:38:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 17, '', '', 0, 813, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(46, '绿色版 xampp 1.6.8 的配制', '-xampp-1-6-8-', '', '<h1>xampp 1.6.8 配置</h1>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>xampp已经出了很多新版本，为什么我还要使用xampp1.6.8呢？只因为它够小巧，可以方便我在各种环境下使用并节省空间，特别是移动存储设备。</p>\r\n<p>xampp1.6.8是1.6最后一版，它的7z自解压版只有32.2M,而安装版也只有37.5M，最新的1.7.7版文件大小增长了很多.</p>\r\n<p>首先,需用127.0.0.1登录并设定MySQL的root密码</p>\r\n<h3>xampp/apache/conf/httpd.conf配置根目录</h3>\r\n<p>找到以下代码：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:176">DocumentRoot "/xampp/htdocs"\r\n</pre>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:203">&lt;Directory "/xampp/htdocs"&gt;\r\n&lt;/Directory&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>更改为：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:176">DocumentRoot "/htdocs"\r\n</pre>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:203">&lt;Directory "/htdocs"&gt;\r\n&lt;/Directory&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>这样可以使服务运行目录降低一层深度并独立出来,便于以后管理.</p>\r\n<h3>xampp/apache/bin/php.ini配置功能扩展</h3>\r\n<p>在此文件中需要配制的项目；</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>如果需要使用sqlite3的pdo的话,需找到如下内容并去掉他的";"注释</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:646">;extension=php_pdo_sqlite.dll\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>重设资源限制</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:240">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;\r\n; Resource Limits ;\r\n;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;\r\n\r\nmax_execution_time = 60     ; Maximum execution time of each script, in seconds\r\nmax_input_time = 60	; Maximum amount of time each script may spend parsing request data\r\nmemory_limit = 32M      ; Maximum amount of memory a script may consume (16MB)\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>xampp/mysql/bin/my.cnf配置数据存储目录</h3>\r\n<p>windows系统下.cnf 默认会被当成快捷方式，看不到扩展名，且无法直接修改。</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:31">datadir="/xampp/mysql/data"\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>修改为：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:31">datadir="/data"\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>这样可以是数据存储目录减少两层深度并独立出来，必满重安装xampp时误删除。</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>如果有需要zend解密的话,可以找到如下内容:</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:1263">[Zend]\r\nzend_extension_ts = "\\xampp\\php\\zendOptimizer\\lib\\ZendExtensionManager.dll"\r\nzend_extension_manager.optimizer_ts = "\\xampp\\php\\zendOptimizer\\lib\\Optimizer"\r\nzend_optimizer.enable_loader = 0\r\nzend_optimizer.optimization_level=15\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>将zend_optimizer.enable_loader = 0的0改为1即可:</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums:1266">zend_optimizer.enable_loader = 1\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>如果要使用ZendGdata，需引入其库路径：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">;;;;;;;;;;;;;\r\n; ZendGdata ;\r\n;;;;;;;;;;;;;\r\ninclude_path = "F:\\htdocs\\ZendGdata\\library"\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>和超级旋风共同使用的80端口占用问题</h3>\r\n<p>超级旋风先于xampp启动，会使xampp无法启动，xampp提示80端口占用，实际上被占用的端口不是80，而是供ssl使用的443，关闭ssl或更改443为别的端口即可。</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-10-01 14:21:29', 1, '', '2013-06-01 13:47:20', 1, 1, '2013-06-01 13:48:24', '2011-10-01 14:21:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 17, 0, 15, '', '', 0, 570, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(47, '用 PHP 操作 SQLite 数据库', '-php-sqlite-', '', '<p>sqlite是个小巧方便的数据库，它相对去其他数据库最大的便利之处在于整个库只有1个文件，容易维护和交换。</p>\r\n<p>常用的sqlite数据库有两个版本，sqlite2和sqlite3，用PHP处理的方法不同。</p>\r\n<h3>sqlite2</h3>\r\n<p>sqlite2被php5的原生支持</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;?php\r\n// set access parameters\r\n$db = "goods.db3";\r\n\r\n$conn= sqlite_open($db) or die ("ERROR: Cannot open database");\r\n\r\n// sqlite_query($conn, "CREATE TABLE employees (ID INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY, Name VARCHAR(255));");\r\nsqlite_query($conn, "INSERT INTO employees (Name) VALUES (''James Fisher'');");\r\nsqlite_query($conn, "INSERT INTO employees (Name) VALUES (''Peter Hutchinson'');");\r\nsqlite_query($conn, "INSERT INTO employees (Name) VALUES (''Richard Hartis'');");\r\n\r\n$sql ="select * from employees";\r\n$result = sqlite_query($conn, $sql) or die("Error in query execution: " . sqlite_error_string(sqlite_last_error($conn)));\r\nif(sqlite_num_rows($result) &gt; 0)\r\n{\r\n	while($row=sqlite_fetch_array($result)){\r\n		echo $row[0] . " (" . $row[1] . ") ";\r\n}\r\n}\r\nsqlite_close($conn);\r\n?&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<h3>sqlite3</h3>\r\n<p>当前使用php操作sqlite3需要启用sqlite pdo，在未来的php6中，sqlite3将被原生支持。</p>\r\n<p>用php操作sqlite3</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;?php\r\n$dsn = ''sqlite:wolf.sq3'';\r\ntry{\r\n      $dbh = new pdo($dsn);\r\n      echo ''PDO Connection OK!''.''&lt;br /&gt;'';\r\n      // $dbh-&gt;exec("create table zzu(id integer,name varchar(255))");\r\n      // echo ''Create Table Ok!''.''&lt;br /&gt;'';\r\n      // $dbh-&gt;exec("insert into zzu values(1,''usen'')");\r\n      // echo ''Insert Data OK!''.''&lt;br /&gt;'';\r\n      $dbh-&gt;beginTransaction();\r\n      $sth = $dbh-&gt;prepare(''select * from page'');\r\n      $sth-&gt;execute();\r\n      $result = $sth-&gt;fetchAll();\r\n      print_r($result);\r\n      $dsn = null;\r\n\r\n}catch (pdoexception $e){\r\n     echo ''Connection failed:''.$e-&gt;getmessage();\r\n     $dsn = null;\r\n}\r\n?&gt;\r\n</pre>', '', 1, 2, 0, 10, 