(48, '常用浏览器的常用配置', '2013-01-16-08-35-05', '', '<h3>网银证书</h3>\r\n<p>有“受信任的根证书颁发机构”和“个人证书”两个区域的证书需安装。</p>\r\n<h3>Page Speed扩展</h3>\r\n<p>适用于Firefox和Chrome的Page Speed扩展下载地址 <a href="http://code.google.com/intl/zh-CN/speed/page-speed/download.html">http://code.google.com/intl/zh-CN/speed/page-speed/download.html</a></p>\r\n<p>由于众所周知的原因，Google服务周期性无法连接，且速度缓慢，建议下载Page Speed后做好备份</p>\r\n<h3>“迅雷精简版”扩展</h3>\r\n<p>适用于Firefox和Chrome的"迅雷精简版"扩展, 可以从MiniThunder的安装文件夹MiniThunder\\bho中获取, crx属Chrome扩展, xpi属Firefox扩展。</p>\r\n<p>xl_plugin_chrome_5.crx是专为Chrome5.0及更老版本提供支持, 高版本则需安装xl_plugin_chrome.crx</p>\r\n<h3>Chrome配置</h3>\r\n<p>Chrome安装Page Speed前，必须在Chrome中访问chrome://flags，找到“实验性扩展程序 API”B并启用它</p>\r\n<p>Chrome安装Page Speed，需右键page-speed.crx文件并选择用Chrome打开，之后选择安装即可。</p>\r\n<p>用账户开启同步功能。</p>\r\n<h3>Firefox配置</h3>\r\n<p>首先要先于Firebug安装Page Speed, 可选安装Web developer。</p>\r\n<p>Firefox安装Page Speed的.xpi文件。须用Firefox的“附加组件管理器-&gt; 从文件安装附加组件”按钮选择安装, 扩展文件为page-speed.xpi。</p>\r\n<p>Firefox安装"迅雷精简版"扩展，同样用Firefox的“附加组件管理器-&gt; 从文件安装附加组件”按钮选择安装，扩展文件为thunder.xpi，不过其暂不支持最新版Firefox。</p>\r\n<p>对下载功能稍作调整:"工具-&gt; 选项-&gt; 总询问保存文件的位置"</p>\r\n<p>用帐号和备份过的密钥开启同步功能。</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-10-02 14:01:40', 1, '', '2011-10-02 14:01:40', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-02 14:01:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 13, '', '', 0, 555, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(49, 'SQLite 管理工具', 'sqlite-', '', '<h3>SQLiteStudio（推荐5星）</h3>\r\n<p>官网：<a href="http://sqlitestudio.one.pl/">http://sqlitestudio.one.pl/</a><br />功能完善的sqlite2和sqlite3工具，视图编码为utf8。</p>\r\n<h3>SQLiteSpy（推荐5星），只识别sqlite3</h3>\r\n<p>官网： <a href="http://www.yunqa.de/delphi/doku.php/products/sqlitespy/">http://www.yunqa.de/delphi/doku.php/products/sqlitespy/</a><br /> 单文件，界面设计紧凑，较稳定,功能较少，创建表与添加数据均需sql语句，快捷键教方便，作为数据浏览和修改工具极佳，试图编码为utf-8，对gbk2312显示乱码。</p>\r\n<h3>Sqlite3Explorer（推荐4星），用于sqlite3</h3>\r\n<p>官网：<a href="http://www.singular.gr/sqlite/">http://www.singular.gr/sqlite/</a><br />但xp下只是别gbk2312编码，界面紧凑，功能全面。</p>\r\n<h3>SQLite Expert Personal（推荐5星），只识别sqlite3</h3>\r\n<p>官网：<a href="http://www.sqliteexpert.com/">http://www.sqliteexpert.com/</a><br /> 个人免费版，软件大于20M，适合作为SQLite数据编辑工具，可以切换试图编码</p>\r\n<h3>SQLite Administrator（3星），只识别sqlite2</h3>\r\n<p>官网：<a href="http://sqliteadmin.orbmu2k.de/">http://sqliteadmin.orbmu2k.de/</a><br /> 功能齐全，界面有多语言，带导出功能，很久未更新，只识别sqlite2，可用于sqlite2到sqlite3的转换，win xp下视图的编码为gbk2312，对utf-8显示乱码。</p>\r\n<h3>SQLite Manager （推荐4星）</h3>\r\n<p>火狐浏览器插件，可以认为有包依赖</p>\r\n<h3>SQLite Database Browser（推荐4星）</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>注意：如果你的PHP文件是以GB2312编码，存入的数据就是GB2312，同样以GB2312编码读取就可以正常显示。而且，在中文Windows下，SQLiteAdmin可以正确看到GB2312编码的数据，不会乱码。</p>\r\n<p>sqlite2转sqlite3命令，反之亦然。有转换工具在手，首选软件当然是5星db3，SQLiteSpy和SQLite Expert Personal配合使用，需导入导出时可以尝试下SQLite Administrator，推荐编码为utf-8。<br /> 注意：sqlite2转sqlite3，有可能出现数字前面的0会被去除的情况！</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">sqlite world.db .dump | sqlite3 world-new.db\r\n</pre>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-10-19 09:52:01', 1, '', '2011-10-19 09:52:01', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-19 09:52:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 8, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 836, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(50, 'MySQL 管理工具', 'mysql-', '', '<p>MySQL GUI Tools（推荐5星）<br /> 官方出品，功能全面，界面紧凑，可从口袋版中提取简体中文语言文件，复制到相应目录即可。</p>\r\n<p>HeidiSQL 免费的，英文的（推荐5星）</p>\r\n<p>http://www.heidisql.com/</p>\r\n<p>Navicat<br /> Navicat 提供商业版 Navicat Premium 和 免费的版本 Navicat Lite 。免费版本的功能已经足够强大了。</p>\r\n<p>MySQL workbench<br /> 有包依赖</p>\r\n<p>上面的是免费的，还有两个收费的<br /> sql-front<br /> SQLyog</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-10-22 06:23:24', 1, '', '2011-10-22 06:23:24', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 06:23:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 10, 'MySQL, 管理工具, GUI, 软件, 数据库', 'MySQL 管理工具', 0, 369, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(51, 'SQLiteSpy 菜单全翻译', 'sqlitespy-', '', '<h3>File<span>[文件]</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New Database<span>[新建数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>Open Datebase<span>[打开数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>Reopen Database<span>[打开最近的数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>Attach Datebase<span>[附加数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>Close Database<span>[关闭数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>New SQL<span>[新建SQL]</span> <strong>Ctrl+N</strong></li>\r\n<li>Open SQL<span>[打开SQL]</span> <strong>Ctrl+O</strong></li>\r\n<li>Reopen SQL<span>[打开最近的SQL]</span></li>\r\n<li>Save SQL<span>[保存SQL]</span> <strong>Ctrl+S</strong></li>\r\n<li>Save SQL As...<span>[另存SQL为……]</span> <strong>Ctrl+Shift+S</strong></li>\r\n<li>Close SQL<span>[关闭SQL]</span> <strong>Ctrl+F4</strong></li>\r\n<li>Exit<span>[退出]</span> <strong>Alt+F4</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Edit<span>[编辑]</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Undo<span>[后退]</span> <strong>Ctrl+Z</strong></li>\r\n<li>Edit Cell<span>[编辑单元格内容]</span> <strong>F2</strong></li>\r\n<li>Cut<span>[剪切]</span> <strong>Ctrl+X</strong></li>\r\n<li>Copy<span>[复制]</span> <strong>Ctrl+C</strong></li>\r\n<li>Paste<span>[粘贴]</span> <strong>Ctrl+V</strong></li>\r\n<li>Delete<span>[删除]</span><strong>Delete</strong></li>\r\n<li>Select All<span>[全选]</span> <strong>Ctrl+A</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>View<span>[查看]</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Clear Data Results<span>[清除数据结果]</span></li>\r\n<li>Refresh Tree<span>[刷新树]</span><strong>F5</strong></li>\r\n<li>Expand Tree<span>[展开树]</span></li>\r\n<li>Collapse Tree<span>[折叠树]</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Execute<span>[执行]</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Execute SQL<span>[执行SQL]</span> <strong>F9</strong></li>\r\n<li>Execute SQL Line<span>[执行单行SQL]</span> <strong>Ctrl+F9</strong></li>\r\n<li>Analyze Database<span>[分析数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>Vacuum Database<span>[清空数据库]</span></li>\r\n<li>Text to Unicode Conversion<span>[编码转换]</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Option<span>[设置]</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Read Only<span>[只读]</span></li>\r\n<li>REGEXP ignores case<span>[正则表达式忽略大小写]</span></li>\r\n<li>Decimal Separator: Full Stop<span>[十进制分隔符：句号]</span></li>\r\n<li>Decimal Separator: Comma<span>[十进制分隔符：逗号]</span></li>\r\n<li>Decimal Separator: User<span>[十进制分隔符：用户]</span></li>\r\n<li>Options<span>[设置]</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Help<span>[帮助]</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>About<span>[关于]</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 6, 0, 17, '2011-10-22 06:30:08', 1, '', '2011-10-22 06:30:08', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 06:30:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 8, '', '', 0, 370, 'robots=\nauthor=');
