(52, 'Zen Coding 的安装与使用', 'zen-coding-', '', '<p>Zen Coding提供了一种创新的、最最高效的html文档编写方式。在使用Zen Coding之前，最好的html编写方式是wiki，wiki提供了一种简洁的编码约定，当按wiki语法录入完一篇文章，提交后将由相应的系统统一转换为html结构。但遗憾的是，wiki语法在不同的wiki系统中并不完全一致。 如今，Zen Coding成为编写html文档的最强解决方案，除了wiki可以内嵌html这一优势，其他方面Zen Coding可以完胜wiki了。Zen Coding已有各种常用代码编辑器的插件版，同时也支持网页版编辑器，通用解决方案意味着在几乎所有场合，你都可以用Zen Coding的相同的录入方式来快速书写html文档。 要鸡蛋里挑骨头的话，我想你也只能说Zen Coding无法像wiki那样直接转换内嵌的html中的&lt;和&gt;代码输出，以及为了避免和各编辑器原有的快捷键产生冲突，致使快捷方式略有区别。</p>\r\n<h2>WordPress有Zen Coding插件可用，直接下载并上传安装即可使用，它的快捷键是：</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>CTRL+E 或 TAB ：这个是展开缩写的代码片断</li>\r\n<li>CTRL+RIGHT：移动光标到下一个编辑点</li>\r\n<li>CTRL+LEFT：移动光标到上一个编辑点</li>\r\n<li>CTRL+D：选择标签外的内容（测试中发现这个功能跟下面一样）</li>\r\n<li>CTRL+SHIFT+D：选择标签内的内容</li>\r\n<li>CTRL+L：选择当前行</li>\r\n<li>CTRL+SHIFT+A：选择一断代码后，按这个组合键，弹包围选中代码的窗口</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>为EmEditor安装Zen Coding，这个安装是最麻烦的</h2>\r\n<h3>To install Zen Coding for the Snippets plug-in</h3>\r\n<h3>译：作为"代码片段插件"安装"Zen Coding"</h3>\r\n<p>1. Copy "zen_emeditor.jsee" to the My Macros folder. The My Macros folder usually exists under the My Documents folder. However, if you have never used macros before, this folder may not exist already. In that case, you can create My Macros folder under the My Documents folder, and then copy the macro into this folder.</p>\r\n<p>译：1.复制"zen_emeditor.jsee"到"My Macros"文件夹。"My Macros"文件夹通常在"我的文档"文件夹中。如果你还没有使用过"宏"，"My Macros"文件夹可能还未创建，那么，你可以在"我的文档"中创建"My Macros"，然后复制Zen Coding宏到对应的"My Macros"文件夹中。</p>\r\n<p>2. If the Snippets custom bar is not visible, Select Snippets on the Tools -&gt; Plug-ins (or click the Snippets button on the Plug-ins Toolbar).</p>\r\n<p>译：2.如果"代码片段栏"未显示，那么就选择"工具"-&gt;"插件"的"代码片段"（或者点击"插件工具栏"的"代码片段"按钮）。</p>\r\n<p>3. Right click on the Snippets custom bar to display a menu.</p>\r\n<p>译：3.右键单击"代码片段"栏以显示菜单。</p>\r\n<p>4. Select Import/Export -&gt; Import to Root...</p>\r\n<p>译：4.选择"导入/导出"-&gt;"导入到根目录……"</p>\r\n<p>5. Select "zen-coding-en.eesnip".</p>\r\n<p>译：5.选择导入项"zen-coding-en.eesnip"。</p>\r\n<p>6. If you wish to use Zen Coding while the Snippets custom bar is hidden, you can right-click on the Snippets button on the Plug-ins Toolbar (or in the Snippets Custom Bar, select View &gt; Plug-in Properties), and click "Run Background".</p>\r\n<p>译：6.如果你希望在"代码片段栏"隐藏是使用zen-coding,你可以右键单击"代码片段栏"，在右键菜单中选择"视图"-&gt;"插件属性"，然后点选"后台运行"。</p>\r\n<p>In the Snippets Custom Bar, you will see a new folder named "Zen Coding", and in this folder you will see 17 new macro items. All of these macros are assigned with shortcut keys:</p>\r\n<p>译：在"代码片段栏"，你将看到一个新的以"Zen Coding"命名的文件夹，在这个文件夹中有17个新的"宏"项目，以下是这些"宏"的快捷键：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>- Balance Tag (Ctrl+Shift+D)</li>\r\n<li>- Decrement number by 0.1 (Ctrl+Shift+Num -)</li>\r\n<li>- Decrement number by 1 (Ctrl+Num -)</li>\r\n<li>- Decrement number by 10 (Shift+Num -)</li>\r\n<li>- Evaluate Math Expression (Ctrl+=)</li>\r\n<li>- Expand Abbreviation (F12)</li>\r\n<li>- Go to Matching Pair (Ctrl+[)</li>\r\n<li>- Increment number by 0.1 (Ctrl+Shift+Num +)</li>\r\n<li>- Increment number by 1 (Ctrl+Num +)</li>\r\n<li>- Increment number by 10 (Shift+Num +)</li>\r\n<li>- Merge Lines (Ctrl+Shift+M)</li>\r\n<li>- Next Edit Point (Ctrl+\\)</li>\r\n<li>- Previous Edit Point (Ctrl+Shift+\\)</li>\r\n<li>- Remove Tag (Ctrl+Shift+'')</li>\r\n<li>- Split/Joint Tag (Ctrl+;)</li>\r\n<li>- Toggle Comment (Alt+/)</li>\r\n<li>- Wrap with Abbreviation (Ctrl+Shift+A)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The shortcut keys described above are for U.S. keyboards. International keyboards may have different key layouts and thus short cuts may be different. You can customize shortcut keys from each snippet properties.</p>\r\n<p>译：以上所述是美式键盘的快捷键，国际化的键盘可能有不同的键盘布局，快捷键可能有些却别，你可以定制每个片段属性的快捷键。</p>\r\n<h3>To install Zen Coding as a direct macro</h3>\r\n<h3>译：作为直接的宏安装Zen Coding</h3>\r\n<p>1. Copy both "zen_emeditor.jsee" and "zen_popup_menu.jsee" to the My Macros folder (usually My Documents\\My Macros).</p>\r\n<p>译：1.同时复制"zen_emeditor.jsee"和"zen_popup_menu.jsee"到"My Macros"文件夹（通常在"My Documents\\My Macros"）。</p>\r\n<p>2. On the Macros menu, click on "Select...", and select "zen_popup_menu.jsee".</p>\r\n<p>译：2.在"宏"菜单，点击"选择……"，然后选择"zen_popup_menu.jsee"。</p>\r\n<p>3. If you wish to assign a keyboard shortcut to run this macro, select "Properties for All Configuration" on the Tools menu. Click the Keyboard tab. Select "My Macros" on the Category drop-down list, and select "zen_popup_menu.jsee". In the "Press New Shortcut Key" text box, press your favorite keyboard shortcut, and click the Assign button.</p>\r\n<p>译：3.如果你希望指定快捷键来运行这个"宏"，选择"工具"-&gt;"所有配置属性"，点选"键盘"选项卡，在"类别"下拉菜单中选择"我的宏"，在"命令"下拉菜单选择"zen_popup_menu.jsee"，在"按下新快捷键"文本框中输入你想要的快捷键，并按"分配"按钮。</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>为PsPad安装Zen Coding</h2>\r\n<p>1.从http://code.google.com/p/zen-coding/downloads/list下载PsPad版的Zen Coding</p>\r\n<p>2.解压下载的.zip格式文件，找到其中一个js文件，并将其放置于PSPad editor安装目录的Script/JScript文件夹中。</p>\r\n<p>3.使用：在PsPad工具栏的"脚本"菜单下可以看到"Zen Coding"目录，各快捷键都有显示，最常用的转换快捷键为"Ctrl+,"</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Expand Abbreviation           Ctrl+,</li>\r\n<li>Wrap with Abbreviation       Ctrl+Shift+Alt+a</li>\r\n<li>Balance Tag                       Ctrl+Alt+d</li>\r\n<li>Balance Tag Inward            Ctrl+Alt+Shift+d</li>\r\n<li>Merge Lines</li>\r\n<li>Next Edit Point</li>\r\n<li>Previous Edit Point</li>\r\n<li>Remove Tag                     Ctrl+''</li>\r\n<li>Split/Join Tag                    Ctrl+Alt+''</li>\r\n<li>Toggle Comment               Ctrl+Alt+;</li>\r\n<li>0.7版分割线</li>\r\n<li>Evaluate Math Expression        Ctrl+y</li>\r\n<li>Increment number by 1          Ctrl+up</li>\r\n<li>Decrement number by 1         Ctrl+down</li>\r\n<li>Increment number by 0.1       Alt+up</li>\r\n<li>Decrement number by 0.1      Alt+down</li>\r\n<li>Increment number by 10        Ctrl+Alt+up</li>\r\n<li>Decrement number by 10       Ctrl+Alt+down</li>\r\n<li>Select Next Item                   Ctrl+.</li>\r\n<li>Select Previous Item              Ctrl+Shift+.</li>\r\n<li>Reflect CSS Value                  Ctrl+Shift+B</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>Dreamweaver安装Zen Coding，双击下载到的mxp文件便自动安装了</h2>\r\n<p>Dreamweaver版Zen Coding的快捷键与PsPad版相同</p>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-10-25 11:58:21', 1, '', '2011-10-25 11:58:21', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-25 11:58:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 10, 'Zen Coding, 工具, 效率, 集成, 安装, 使用, 软件, PsPad, EmEditor, Dreamweaver, 插件, 扩展', 'Zen Coding 的安装与使用', 0, 872, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(53, 'Tabbed 设计思路', 'tabbed-', '', '<pre class="prettyprint">.tabbed { position:relative; border:1px solid #000; width:800px; }\r\n.tabbed ul { position:relative; }\r\n.tabbed ul li { display:inline; border:1px solid #000; }\r\n/* 二级ul相对于一级停靠 */\r\n.tabbed ul li ul { position:absolute; top:20px; left:0; width:100%; border:1px solid #369; display:none; }\r\n.tabbed ul li ul li { position:static; display:block; float:none; border:0; }\r\n.tabbed ul li .more { position:absolute; top:-20px; right:0; }\r\n.tabbed ul li.active { }\r\n.tabbed ul li.active ul { display:block; }\r\n.tabbed ul li.active ul li { display:block; }\r\n</pre>', '', 1, 7, 0, 16, '2011-11-09 02:15:18', 1, '', '2011-11-09 02:15:18', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-09 02:15:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 8, 'Tabbed, 设计, HTML, CSS, 参考, 代码片段', 'Tabbed 设计思路', 0, 330, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(54, 'ecshop index.js 修改', 'ecshop-index-js-', '', '<p>index.js文件</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">function change_tab_style(item, elem, obj)\r\n{\r\n    elem = elem.toUpperCase();\r\n    var itemObj = document.getElementById(item);\r\n    var elems = itemObj.getElementsByTagName(elem);\r\n    var _o = obj.parentNode;\r\n    while(_o.nodeName != elem)\r\n    {\r\n        _o = _o.parentNode;\r\n    }\r\n    for (var i=0,l=elems.length; i&lt;l; i++)\r\n    {\r\n        elems[i].className = ''h2bg'';\r\n    }\r\n    _o.className = '''';\r\n}\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>修改className</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint">function change_tab_style(item, elem, obj)\r\n{\r\n    elem = elem.toUpperCase();\r\n    var itemObj = document.getElementById(item);\r\n    var elems = itemObj.getElementsByTagName(elem);\r\n    var _o = obj.parentNode;\r\n    while(_o.nodeName != elem)\r\n    {\r\n        _o = _o.parentNode;\r\n    }\r\n    for (var i=0,l=elems.length; i&lt;l; i++)\r\n    {\r\n        elems[i].className = ''off'';\r\n    }\r\n    _o.className = ''on'';\r\n}\r\n</pre>', '', 1, 5, 0, 7, '2011-11-12 05:08:19', 1, '', '2011-11-12 05:08:19', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-12 05:08:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 4, 'ecshop index.js 修改', 'ecshop index.js 修改', 0, 384, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(55, 'SQLite 重要语句', 'sqlite-', '', '<h3>SQLite 创建当前时间列（格林尼治标准时间）</h3>\r\n<p>当前时间列，由于默认的时间是以格林尼治标准时间为基准的，因此在中国使用的话会正好早8个小时。</p>\r\n<p>方法1：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">create table log(\r\n	content varchar(256),\r\n	logtime datetime default (datetime(''now''))\r\n)\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>方法2：</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">create table log(\r\n	content varchar(256),\r\n	logtime TIMESTAMP default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\r\n)\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>SQLite 创建当前时间列（中国时间）</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">create table log(\r\n	content varchar(256),\r\n	logtime TIMESTAMP default (datetime(''now'', ''localtime''))\r\n)\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>SQLite 查询数据库中包含哪些表</h3>\r\n<p>注意：这个查询涉及特殊的表“sqlite_master”，它通常不可见，在这个表中记录着涉及各个表结构的所有信息,另外，还有一个特殊的表是“sqlite_sequence”。</p>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">SELECT * FROM sqlite_master WHERE type = "table" AND tbl_name != "sqlite_sequence"\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>当数据库中包含自动编号的字段时，SQLite会自动建立一个名为“sqlite_sequence”的表。这个表包含两个字段：name 和 seq 。name字段记录了自动编号字段所在的表，seq字段记录了当前用到的序号（下一条记录的编号就是当前序号加1）。</p>\r\n<h3>SQLite 增加一行记录</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">INSERT INTO 商品表 (''ID'') VALUES (NULL)\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<h3>SQLite 增加列</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">ALTER TABLE t ADD time TIMESTAMP DEFAULT(datetime(''now'', ''localtime''))\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<h3>SQLite 删除列，不能直接删除</h3>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">CREATE TABLE t2 AS SELECT id FROM t1;\r\nDROP TABLE t1;\r\nALTER TABLE t2 RENAME TO t1;\r\n\r\n</pre>', '', 1, 3, 0, 5, '2011-12-06 02:49:05', 1, '', '2011-12-06 02:49:05', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-06 02:49:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 682, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(56, '工商注册完成', '2013-01-16-08-36-34', '', '<p>2011年12月16日下午，办理了工商注册。</p>\r\n<p>按照规定，1月1日需审照，按照工商所工作人员的建议，等到了2012年再去领执照，可以节省支出和避免麻烦。</p>\r\n<p>以此为契机，我们开始新的征程。</p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 2, '2011-12-17 12:38:13', 1, '', '2011-12-17 12:38:13', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-17 12:38:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 9, '', '', 0, 695, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(57, 'Joomla! 2012 年发行计划（Joomla! 2.5）', 'joomla-2012-joomla-2-5', '', '<h2>Joomla! 2012发行计划发布</h2>\r\n<p>JOOMLA 2.5.0 GA（一般情况而定）将于2012年1月10日或前后公布。</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h3>在此日期后的计划的一个里程碑是：</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>2012年2月10日 - JOOMLA 1.7到达生命的终点，并不再支持</li>\r\n<li>2012年4月 - JOOMLA 1.5到达生命的终点</li>\r\n<li>2012年7月 - 发布下一个版本的Joomla</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>请注意，日期可能会受到志愿者和非我们所能控制的情况下的可用性而改变。</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-sg6Zsvjwcvw/TvQTcxBs0iI/AAAAAAAAHHw/gMPdjNBIdK8/s800/screens.png" border="0" alt="Joomla! 2.5" width="557" height="351" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>从以上官方信息我们可以获知：</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>之前各种消息中提到的Joomla! 1.8长期支持版不存在，而Joomla! 2.5是接替Joomla! 1.5的下一个长期支持版，支持期为至少18个月，版本号将由1.7直接跳至2.5。</li>\r\n<li>与此前的Joomla! 1.6和Joomla! 1.7不同，它们只是基于新Joomla! 框架对1.5的重现，而在Joomla! 2.5 Beta1中我们已经可以看到功能方面的扩展。</li>\r\n<li>Joomla! 2.5 Beta1中可见后台管理界面细节错误已修复，貌似已经做好了出来见人的准备。</li>\r\n<li>Joomla! 1.7可以直接升级迁移到Joomla! 2.5，而Joomla! 1.5升级迁移到Joomla! 2.5需要借助jUpgrade组件。</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 4, 0, 12, '2011-12-23 05:11:34', 1, '', '2011-12-23 05:11:34', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-23 05:11:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 4, 'Joomla!, 2012年, 发行计划, 2.5版', 'Joomla! 2012 年发行计划（Joomla! 2.5）', 0, 475, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(58, '步步街网络服务中已做好向新版本内核迁移的准备', '2013-01-16-08-36-56', '', '<p>步步街银川网络服务中心已做好向新版本内核迁移的准备.</p>\r\n<p>作为开发者我们需要时刻走在技术前沿,在向前发展的过程中,我们需要顾及向后兼容,同时为面向未来的技术迭代更新做好准备,以便在未来的某个时机,快速转换到新的标准下.</p>\r\n<p>开发服务的提供者最需要的是长期的技术与标准积累,面对"流水的兵",我们需要创建"铁打的营盘",让长期积累与总结的优势持续下去,避免出现断层.我们决心一直走在技术前沿,而瞻前顾后是我们运用技术的遵旨.</p>\r\n<p>开发工具仅仅是定式的工具而已,最重要的开发工具是总结出的规则与流程,以及这个总结与整理的习惯,它是最智能的开发工具.</p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 2, '2011-12-25 09:31:14', 1, '', '2011-12-25 09:31:14', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-25 09:31:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 10, '', '', 0, 742, 'robots=\nauthor='),
