(128, 'ContentBuilder设置项', 'contentbuiler-options', '', '<div style="clear:both;">\r\n<h2>Data storage（数据存储）</h2>\r\n<table class="tbl" style="float:left;" border="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope="col">Details</th> <th scope="col">New Filds</th> <th scope="col">Data Table</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Name</li>\r\n<li>Title</li>\r\n<li>Update From CSV                 \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Upload File</li>\r\n<li>drop existing records</li>\r\n<li>Auto Publish</li>\r\n<li>delimiter</li>\r\n<li>Repair Encoding*</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Name</li>\r\n<li>Title</li>\r\n<li>Group</li>\r\n<li>Group definition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ID</li>\r\n<li>Name</li>\r\n<li>Title</li>\r\n<li>Group                 \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Edit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Order by</li>\r\n<li>Published</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>网页交互字段有两种形式，表单形式的和数据库形式的，前者用于展现，后者用于存储。为了方便处理，ContentBuilder将MySQL数据库中存储的字段类型统一设定成text形式，所以在"字段"的理解上不再受其干扰。</p>\r\n<p>通常ContentBuilder中所提到的"字段"只是表单字段。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br style="clear:both;" /></p>\r\n<hr style="clear:both;" />\r\n<div style="clear:both;">\r\n<h2>Views Manager（视图管理）</h2>\r\n<table class="tbl" border="1" summary="j">\r\n<caption> </caption> \r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope="col">View<br /> (全局设置)</th> <th scope="col">List<br /> intro text<br /> (列表<br /> 简介)</th> <th scope="col">List Stabus<br /> (列表状态)</th> <th scope="col">\r\n<p>Content <br /> Template <br /> (内容模板)</p>\r\n</th> <th scope="col"> Content <br /> Prepare </th> <th scope="col"> Editable<br /> Template<br /> (编辑模板)</th> <th scope="col"> Editable<br /> Prepare </th> <th scope="col">\r\n<p>Email <br /> Template<br /> (邮件模板)</p>\r\n</th> <th scope="col"> Permissions<br /> (权限)</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Source                 \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Name</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ID</li>\r\n<li>Lable</li>\r\n<li>Include in list</li>\r\n<li>